ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project focuses on cleaning and preprocessing raw customer data using Python and Pandas. The notebook demonstrates how to transform messy, inconsistent data into a clean, structured, and analysis-ready dataset.

The project covers common real-world data issues such as duplicates, inconsistent formatting, missing values, and invalid records.

